&lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; is a 1984 malayalam film written by padmarajan and directed by i. v. sasi . it stars mammootty , rahman , lalu alex , shobhana and seema . this film won 1984 kerala state film awards for the best story ( padmarajan ) , best music director ( shyam ) and best female singer ( s. janaki ) . the story was an adaptation of the 1912 novel daddy-long-legs by jean webster .